window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>💎<b>Collector’s Edition — The Eight-Book Blood Saga —</b>Over <b>half a million words</b> of dark romance, danger and redemption—an unforgettable journey from the first heartbeat... to the last. <b><i>Save 50% over individual price!</i></b><br><br>🔥<b>TRUE BLOOD &amp; ACOTAR meet TWILIGHT</b>—8 Books, <i><b>Nearly 3,000 Pages </b>of Dark Fantasy Romance!</i>🔥</p><ul><li>⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ <b>\"I really enjoyed the series and could not put it down!!\"</b> <i>~ Suzanne P.</i></li></ul><p><br>🩸<b>A Love That Shakes Worlds. A Destiny That Cannot Be Denied.</b><br><br>From <b><i>New York Times</i>, USA TODAY, Amazon Top-15 and #1 Dark Fantasy Bestseller Tamara Rose Blodgett</b> comes a <b>gripping saga of love, war, and supernatural power</b>, where vampires and werewolves clash over <b>one girl's blood—and the fate of their species.</b></p><p>🖤 <b>WHAT’S INSIDE:</b></p><p>⚔️ <b>BLOOD SINGERS (4.2★)</b> – Julia Wade, a young widow, is <b>thrust into an ancient war</b> between vampires and werewolves. <b>Hunted for her bloodline</b>, she must harness newfound powers and forge her own fate.</p><p>🎶 <b>BLOOD SONG (4.4★)</b> – Trapped in a <b>gilded cage</b>, Julia battles against the <b>forces seeking to control her</b>. As secrets unravel, she faces <b>danger, deception, and a deadly choice.</b></p><p>👑 <b>BLOOD CHOSEN (4.3★)</b> – As Julia struggles to <b>unite warring species</b>, a <b>rival queen emerges</b>, threatening to tear apart the fragile peace. Can she protect those she loves before war consumes them all?</p><p>🔥 <b>BLOOD REIGN (4.5★)</b> – With <b>feuds and rivalries spiraling into chaos</b>, Julia must <b>rally her allies and confront the forces of darkness</b> before it’s too late.</p><p>👼 <b>ANGELIC BLOOD (4.5★)</b> – As supernatural realms descend into <b>all-out war</b>, Julia fights against <b>unimaginable evil</b>. Will her strength be enough to <b>conquer the darkness</b> or will betrayal cost her everything?</p><p>🔮 <b>BLOOD ENCHANTMENT (4.6★)</b> – Trapped in a <b>deadly game of survival</b>, Julia must <b>navigate treacherous alliances, uncover secrets, and face her greatest fears</b>.</p><p>🛡️ <b>REDEMPTIVE BLOOD (4.5★)</b> – Adi and Slash <b>seek refuge in a world where danger lurks behind every shadow</b>. Will redemption be possible—or will their pasts seal their fate?</p><p>👑 <b>BLOOD CROWN (4.4★)</b> – Jacqueline and Domi <b>fight unrest in the fey realm</b>, while Tahlia’s fate hangs in the balance. Can they survive the upheaval, or will their enemies strike first?</p><p>🖤 <b>WHY READERS LOVE THIS SERIES:</b><br>✔️ <b>A sweeping dark fantasy saga with unpredictable twists &amp; breathtaking romance</b><br>✔️ <b>Complex characters, pulse-pounding action, and deeply emotional stakes</b><br>✔️ <b>For fans of True Blood, Twilight, &amp; ACOTAR—intense, atmospheric, and unputdownable</b><br>✔️ <b>A binge-worthy experience—eight full-length novels in one irresistible collection</b></p><p>🩸 <b>Tropes You’ll Crave:</b><br>Dark fantasy romance, supernatural warriors, alpha heroes, vampire strongholds, supernatural showdowns, mixed heritage, forbidden desires, perilous journeys, fiery connections, secrets &amp; revelations, dark romance, enemies-to-lovers, protectors, romantic suspense, slow burn, survival, vengeance.</p><p>📢 <b>DON’T MISS OUT—this collection is a limited-time deal!</b> Click <b>DOWNLOAD NOW</b> and immerse yourself in <b>a world of passion, danger, and destiny today!</b> 🖤</p>"; 
